snippet.title: Backrooms Exploration (Mistcloud Games) // The Mini Indie Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Traverse your way through this Atmospheric Psychological Horror! Explore the 9 eerie levels of The Backrooms, a place where everything seems familiar, with a constant feeling of something or someone watching you. Why were you chosen to enter The Backrooms?

Buy Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1730930/Backrooms_Exploration/

The Mini Indie Showcase 2023: https://youtu.be/ANsVkLxB3e0 

Learn more: https://sixoneindie.com/showcase
